    'FontSize',19,'FontName',fnt,'FontWeight','bold');
ylabel('Pressure Coefficient, C_p', ...
    'FontSize',19,'FontName',fnt,'FontWeight','bold');
title('Chordwise C_p Distribution', ...
    'FontSize',21,'FontName',fnt,'FontWeight','bold');
subtitle(['Final Optimised vs Baseline NACA 4415  |  ' ...
